---
---

<section class="section section-light">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label">The Reality</div>
    <h2>Most agencies think they're secure because nothing bad has happened.</h2>
    <div class="reality-content">
      <div class="reality-left fade-up">
        <p>But here's what we see regularly:</p>
        <ul class="pain-list">
          <li>
            <div class="pain-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg></div>
            Backups exist &mdash; but no one has tested restoring AMS or shared drives
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="pain-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg></div>
            MFA is partially enforced
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="pain-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg></div>
            Former employees still have access
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="pain-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg></div>
            No documented security review in the last 12 months
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="pain-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/></svg></div>
            Carrier cyber questionnaires are getting stricter every year
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="reality-callout fade-up">
        <h3>Cyber risk isn't theoretical anymore.</h3>
        <p>Carriers are asking harder questions. Compliance expectations are rising. And agencies are expected to prove &mdash; not assume &mdash; their security posture.</p>
        <div class="callout-stat">
          <div class="callout-stat-item">
            <span class="num">82%</span>
            <span class="label">of breaches involve<br />human element</span>
          </div>
          <div class="callout-stat-item">
            <span class="num">$4.5M</span>
            <span class="label">avg. cost of<br />a data breach</span>
          </div>
          <div class="callout-stat-item">
            <span class="num">277</span>
            <span class="label">days avg. to identify<br />a breach</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .reality-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  .reality-left p {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .reality-left p:first-child {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .pain-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }

  .pain-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .pain-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    background: rgba(244, 128, 33, 0.1);
    border-radius: 6px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  .pain-icon svg {
    width: 14px;
    height: 14px;
    fill: var(--orange);
  }

  .reality-callout {
    background: var(--light-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 40px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--orange);
  }

  .reality-callout h3 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--charcoal);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .reality-callout p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .callout-stat {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 28px;
    padding-top: 28px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .callout-stat-item {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .callout-stat-item .num {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--orange);
    display: block;
  }

  .callout-stat-item .label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-light);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .reality-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
    .callout-stat {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
  }
</style>
